title: Episode 87: Ft. Safaree Samuels
itunes:title: Episode 87: Ft. Safaree Samuels
description:
This weeks Lip Service features Safaree Samuels! The ladies get straight to it as they get him to open up about his several different rumored "relationships" after Nicki Minaj, why he prefers a monogamous relationship, how long should you wait to delete an ex from your social media and whether or not you should exchange passwords with your partner. Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire, Stephanie Santiago, and Lore'l get him to recall a certain situation that occurred at Sean Kingston house, keeping tally of sex partner
